---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Feliks Mamczur and Prompted Psyche, a research-driven project on AI, cyberpsychology and Human-AI Interaction."
>
  <section class="page-shell two-column">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>Prompted Psyche is Feliks Mamczur's work on the human side of AI.</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        Feliks Mamczur is an author and consultant working at the intersection of
        artificial intelligence, cyberpsychology and Human-AI Interaction.
      </p>
      <p>
        Prompted Psyche is a research-driven publication and consulting hub about how
        artificial intelligence shapes thought, emotion, trust, communication,
        relationships, creativity and work.
      </p>
      <p>
        The project looks at AI literacy, the psychology of working with generative tools,
        trust and decision-making, conversational systems, creative practice, and the
        cultural changes that appear when machines become part of everyday communication.
      </p>
      <p>
        Feliks' background in film and post-production supports this perspective through
        attention to narrative, image, emotion, communication and creative workflow. It
        helps explain why AI is not only a technical system, but also a medium that changes
        how people notice, decide, express and collaborate.
      </p>
      <p>
        Prompted Psyche is not a film portfolio. Film experience is part of the lens, while
        the central subject remains AI, cyberpsychology and Human-AI Interaction.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
